body:
TYRUS -

I WANT TO WRITE A FIC WHERE TJ IS SO POSITIVE THAT THEY WILL KNOW EACH OTHER FOR A LONG TIME THAT HE GETS A TIN/BOX THING TO MAKE AS A TIME CAPSULE AND HE PUTS SOMETHING CUTE IN THEIR LIKE MAYBE SOMETHING FROM A CARNIVAL THAT THEY WON OR IDK SHSJSJ AND THEN CYRUS IS LIKE “IDK WHAT TO GIVE TO YOU TO PUT IN THERE” AND TJ IS LIKE “ANYTHING YOU GIVE ME I’LL BE HAPPY ABOUT” (bear in mind they aren’t dating at this moment) AND SO CYRUS GETS A LIGHTBULB PING ABOVE HIS HEAD AND SMILES BEFORE SAYING “WAIT ONE SECOND DON’T MOVE” AND HE RUNS TO GET HIS POLAROID CAMERA (idk where they are, the park? his garden? idk bro) AND THEN HE RUNS BACK AND TJ’S LIKE “ARE YOU SURE YOU WANNA PUT THAT IN THERE ITS PRETTY EXPENS-“ AND THEN CYRUS CUTS HIM OFF WITH A KISS TAKING A PHOTO IN THE PROCESS AND THEN CYRUS PULLS AWAY AND TJ STILL HAS HIS EYES CLOSED LIKE HE’S SAVORING THE MOMENT AND HE CANT BELIEVE THAT HIS CRUSH OF TWO YEARS JUST KISSED HIM AND SO MANY THOUGHTS ARE RUNNING THROUGH HIS HEAD LIKE ‘IS THIS JUST A PITY KISS’ OR ‘DOES HE KNOW I LIKE HIM?’ OR EVEN ‘DOES HE LIKE ME BACK?’ AND THEN CYRUS TAKES THE POLAROID AND GRABS TJ’S HAND AND PLACES IT IN IT AND TJ SLOWLY OPENS HIS EYES AND LOOKS DOWN AT IT BEFORE LOOKING BACK UP AT CYRUS AND SMILING HESITANTLY, CYRUS SMILES WILDLY AND THEN TJ SAYS QUIETLY “BUT… I WANNA KEEP THIS, I DONT WANT IT TO BE IN THE GROUND FOR TEN YEARS BEFORE I CAN HAHE IT AGAIN” AND CYRYS SAYS “WELL..HOW ABOUT YOU KEEP THIS ONE AND…WE CAN TAKE ANOTHER ONE?” TJ SMILES EVEN WIDER AND SAYS “AND ANOTHER?” CYRUS GIGGLES AND SAYS “AND AS MANY AS YOU WANT.” AND THEN TJ PICKS HIM UP AND SPINS HIM AROUND AND CYRUS IS GIGGLING AND SQUEALING THE WHOLE TIME, TJ IS LAUGHING AND ITS ALL FLUFFY AND THEN TJ PUTS HIM DOWN, THEY’RE SUPER CLOSE AND HE SAYS “Y’KNOW…IT’D BE EASIER TO TAKE MORE PHOTOS IF WE WERE…IF WE-“

“WERE BOYFRIENDS?”

“YEAH, IF WE WERE BOYFRIENDS.”

“DO YOU WANNA BE?”

“OF COURSE…DO YOU?”

“IS THAT EVEN A QUESTION?”

“SO….”

“YES. THAT’S A YES.”

body: i, for one, am happy we have another hiatus after 313. It means the show has longer to gain a bigger audience (especially after the publicity from the most recent episode) for a still possible (however slim) season 4 pick up. And if not, we at least get a good couple more months of this show, with the finale happening over the summer when more people have free time to watch and contribute to the fandom!

summary: There’s something so incredibly tender about the fact that 2/3 of Cyrus’s coming out scenes have taken place at pivotal Jewish...
body: There’s something so incredibly tender about the fact that 2/3 of Cyrus’s coming out scenes have taken place at pivotal Jewish moments in his life. Like Terri Minsky is a Jewish woman showing viewers that u can be very religious and gay at the same time and also like showing this symbolism of Cyrus’s gayness being just as important and innate to him as his Jewishness. It rly shows that both these parts of him are important parts of himself that he was born into and it’s all so intertwined and significant and rly just so special.

summary:

2/3 poc main characters
A GAY...
body:
People who say the “new Disney Channel” sucks clearly haven’t watched Andi Mack. This show has:

  • 2/3 poc main characters
  • A GAY MAIN CHARACTER
  • anxiety/panic attacks storyline
  • jewish representation
  • 3 coming out scenes (so far!!) (and they used the word GAY!)
  • a deaf character + sign language
  • learning disabilities
  • so many biracial couples
  • teen pregnancy/young mother
  • healthy friendships
  • chinese culture representation
  • feminism
  • a whole episode about privilege and inequality!
  • parents in the military (and the effects of their deployment)

Y’all just love to hate, but Andi Mack is literally fantastic and giving you no reason to hate at all. So chill with those generalizations and do yourself a favour: watch Andi Mack.
